---
title: Chickens
author: temujin
tags: [features]
---
Chickens are an animal farmers can have on land to gather eggs from numerous times a day. The eggs can be eaten as is for base stats, but can also be improved on by bringing to a cooking station to create various delicious recipes!

Chickens can also be slaughtered for their carcass. Doing so will be permanent however & the player will have to seek out a breeder to purchase replacement stock for coin. These carcasses can be brought to a butcher shop to create various cuts of chicken meat, where the end products can again be brought to a cooking station to create various delicious recipes!

**Price:** CXP or Bred using a Chicken Coop<br>
**Markeplace Listing**: CXP Store Only / In-World<br>

**Required Tool:** Small Basket<br>
**Durability Use:** 1<br>
**Energy Use:** 5 Pot<br>
**Growth Speed:** 6 hrs

